        </style></head><body style="font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#x27;Segoe UI&#x27;, Roboto, &#x27;Helvetica Neue&#x27;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;color:#44403C;margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#FAFAF9;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%" data-x-apple-data-detectors="false"><div style="display:none;max-height:0;overflow:hidden;font-size:1px;line-height:1px;color:#FAFAF9">No rush — your Medical Certificate request is still here ⏱️ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌ ‌</div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%;background-color:#FAFAF9"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:48px 16px"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" class="email-card" style="max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;background-color:#ffffff;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #E5E5E5;box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:40px 40px 24px 40px;text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au" style="text-decoration:none;display:inline-block"><img src="https://instantmed.com.au/branding/logo.png" alt="InstantMed — Australian telehealth" width="90" height="auto" style="display:block;border:0;outline:none;max-width:90px;height:auto"/></a></td></tr><tr><td style="padding:0 40px"><div style="border-top:1px solid #F5F5F4"></div></td></tr><tr><td class="email-content" style="padding:32px 40px 40px 40px;background-color:#ffffff"><h1 style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:#1C1917;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.5px">Your request is still here</h1><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:15px;color:#44403C;line-height:1.6">Hi Test,</p><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:15px;color:#44403C;line-height:1.6">You started a <strong>Medical Certificate</strong> request about 2 hours ago but didn&#x27;t finish checkout. No worries — everything is saved and ready when you are.</p><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:24px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/request?resume=test" style="display:inline-block;padding:16px 36px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(13,148,136,0.25);background-color:#0D9488;color:#ffffff">Resume your request</a></td></tr></tbody></table><div style="background-color:#F5F5F4;border:1px solid #E5E5E5;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 24px;margin:24px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1C1917;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px">What happens next</h3><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;color:#44403C;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;list-style-type:disc"><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">A doctor reviews your request (usually within an hour)</li><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">You&#x27;ll receive your document via email</li><li style="margin-bottom:0;padding-left:4px">No phone call required for most requests</li></ul></div><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:13px;color:#A8A29E;line-height:1.6">If you&#x27;ve already completed your request or no longer need it, you can safely ignore this email.</p><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:13px;color:#A8A29E;line-height:1.6">Questions? Reply to this email or visit our <a href="https://instantmed.com.au/contact" style="color:#0D9488;font-weight:500">help centre</a>.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:32px 40px;border-top:1px solid #F5F5F4;background-color:#FAFAF9"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:12px;color:#78716C;line-height:1.8"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#78716C;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E5E5E5">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#78716C;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E5E5E5">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/contact" style="color:#78716C;text-decoration:none">Contact</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E5E5E5">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/account?tab=notifications" style="color:#78716C;text-decoration:none">Preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:12px;color:#78716C">Made with care in Australia 🌤️</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#A8A29E;letter-spacing:0.02em">InstantMed Pty Ltd · ABN 64 694 559 334</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html>"
`;

