,</p><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:15px;color:#44403C;line-height:1.6">It&#x27;s been about 30 days since your last <strong>Salbutamol</strong> prescription. If you&#x27;re running low, you can request a repeat through InstantMed.</p><div style="background-color:#F5F5F4;border:1px solid #E5E5E5;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 24px;margin:24px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1C1917;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px">How it works</h3><ul style="padding-left:20px;margin:8px 0;color:#1C1917"><li style="margin-bottom:6px;font-size:14px">Click the button below to start your repeat request</li><li style="margin-bottom:6px;font-size:14px">Your details are pre-filled from last time</li><li style="margin-bottom:6px;font-size:14px">A doctor reviews and sends your eScript within hours</li></ul></div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:24px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/request?type=repeat-script" style="display:inline-block;padding:16px 36px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(13,148,136,0.25);background-color:#0D9488;color:#ffffff">Renew my prescription</a></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:13px;color:#A8A29E;line-height:1.6">Questions? Reply to this email or visit our <a href="https://instantmed.com.au/contact" style="color:#0D9488;font-weight:500">help centre</a>. You can unsubscribe from reminders in your <a href="https://instantmed.com.au/patient/settings" style="color:#0D9488;font-weight:500">account settings</a>.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:32px 40px;border-top:1px solid #F5F5F4;background-color:#FAFAF9"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:12px;color:#78716C;line-hei