<p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#A8A29E">Medical Certificate — $19.95</p></div><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:15px;color:#44403C;line-height:1.6">Hi Test,</p><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:15px;color:#44403C;line-height:1.6">Payment confirmed — your <strong>Medical Certificate</strong> request is now with a doctor for review. Most requests are wrapped up within a couple of hours, and we&#x27;ll email you the moment there&#x27;s an update.</p><div style="background-color:#F5F5F4;border:1px solid #E5E5E5;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 24px;margin:24px 0"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="padding:12px 0;color:#78716C;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #F5F5F4">Reference</td><td style="padding:12px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:400;font-family:inherit;text-align:right;color:#1C1917;border-bottom:1px solid #F5F5F4;letter-spacing:inherit">REQ-TEST</td></tr><tr><td style="padding:12px 0;color:#78716C;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #F5F5F4">Amount paid</td><td style="padding:12px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:400;font-family:inherit;text-align:right;color:#1C1917;border-bottom:1px solid #F5F5F4;letter-spacing:inherit">$19.95</td></tr><tr><td style="padding:12px 0;color:#78716C;font-size:14px;border-bottom:1px solid #F5F5F4">Status</td><td style="padding:12px 0;font-size:14px;font-weight:400;font-family:inherit;text-align:right;color:#1C1917;border-bottom:1px solid #F5F5F4;letter-spacing:inherit">In review</td></tr></tbody></table></div><div style="background-color:#F5F5F4;border:1px solid #E5E5E5;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 24px;margin:24px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1C1917;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px">What happens next</h3><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;color:#44403C;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;list-style-type:disc"><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">A doctor reviews your request (typically 1–2 hou