re documents you need — from your phone, on your schedule.</p><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:15px;color:#44403C;line-height:1.6">No waiting rooms. No phone tag with receptionists. Just fill in a form and a real doctor reviews it.</p><div style="background-color:#F5F5F4;border:1px solid #E5E5E5;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 24px;margin:24px 0"><h3 style="margin:0 0 10px 0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1C1917;line-height:1.5;letter-spacing:-0.1px">Here&#x27;s what you can do</h3><ul style="margin:0;padding-left:20px;color:#44403C;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;list-style-type:disc"><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">Get medical certificates reviewed by a doctor within hours</li><li style="margin-bottom:8px;padding-left:4px">Request prescriptions from registered Australian doctors</li><li style="margin-bottom:0;padding-left:4px">Access specialist consultations online</li></ul></div><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="margin:24px auto;width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/start" style="display:inline-block;padding:16px 36px;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;letter-spacing:0.01em;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(13,148,136,0.25);background-color:#0D9488;color:#ffffff">Get Started</a></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:13px;color:#A8A29E;line-height:1.6">Questions? Reply to this email or visit our <a href="https://instantmed.com.au/contact" style="color:#0D9488;font-weight:500">help centre</a>.</p></td></tr><tr><td class="email-footer" style="padding:32px 40px;border-top:1px solid #F5F5F4;background-color:#FAFAF9"><table role="presentation" cellPadding="0" cellSpacing="0" style="width:100%"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align:center"><p style="margin:0 0 16px 0;font-size:12px;color:#78716C;line-height:1.8"><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/privacy" style="color:#78716C;text-decoration:none">Privacy</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E5E5E5">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/terms" style="color:#78716C;text-decoration:none">Terms</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E5E5E5">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/contact" style="color:#78716C;text-decoration:none">Contact</a><span style="margin:0 8px;color:#E5E5E5">·</span><a href="https://instantmed.com.au/account?tab=notifications" style="color:#78716C;text-decoration:none">Preferences</a></p><p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:12px;color:#78716C">Made with care in Australia 🌤️</p><p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:#A8A29E;letter-spacing:0.02em">InstantMed Pty Ltd · ABN 64 694 559 334</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></body></html>"
